Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.35,0:00:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Brothers and sisters,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.35,0:00:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,welcome to this update!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.29,0:00:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Omicron variant of the COVID-19 virus
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,has quickly spread throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The number of cases has exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We’re saddened to report
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,that as of Friday, January 21,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.91,0:00:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,26,813 of our brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,have now died from COVID-19.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But there have been\Nsome encouraging developments.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,For those who are vaccinated,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,cases of Omicron are generally milder
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.69,0:00:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and have not led to hospitalization or death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, you may have heard reports
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that there has been a major outbreak\Nof Omicron in Puerto Rico.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You may also know that Puerto Rico
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,has a very high rate of vaccination.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Although 551 cases were reported
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,among our brothers\Nduring the recent outbreak,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,only three of our brothers have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.32,0:01:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is our understanding that all of them
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,had serious underlying health issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.29,0:01:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Even one death is too many,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.19,0:01:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,yet we’re relieved that so few died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Our hearts go out to all\Nwho have lost loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.90,0:01:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please continue to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The pandemic is not over,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and we need to continue\Nto take practical steps
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect our lives and our health.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.41,0:01:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition to the pandemic,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.72,0:01:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it has been sobering\Nto watch recent world events unfold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.79,0:01:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We see one natural disaster after another,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.59,0:01:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and we hear threats of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,“The king of the north”\Nand “the king of the south”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.10,0:01:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,continue “pushing” one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.03,0:01:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,When we hear all these things\Nhappening in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it reminds us how vital it is\Nthat we “keep on the watch”.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.71,0:02:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to stay awake spiritually
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and not doze off or get distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.45,0:02:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we are living\Nin the most critical time in human history.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus knew that the last days\Nwould bring challenges
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,that would test our spiritual focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.36,0:02:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of his deep love, he urged his followers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.26,0:02:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as recorded at Luke chapter 21
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.43,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,verses 34-36:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,“But pay attention to yourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.27,0:02:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,“that your hearts never become weighed down
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.21,0:02:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,“with overeating and heavy drinking\Nand anxieties of life,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,“and suddenly that day\Nbe instantly upon you as a snare.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,“For it will come upon all those dwelling\Non the face of the whole earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,“Keep awake, then,\Nall the time making supplication
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.50,0:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,“that you may succeed\Nin escaping all these things
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that must occur and in standing\Nbefore the Son of man.”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We constantly hear encouraging reports
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.77,0:03:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,that you dear brothers and sisters\Nare working hard to “keep awake”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.38,0:03:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and remain busy in your service to Jehovah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You’re busy in your personal ministry
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.92,0:03:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,—writing letters, making phone calls,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and looking for opportunities\Nto share the good news informally—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.49,0:03:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and many were able to auxiliary pioneer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.43,0:03:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,during the recent campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying busy in Jehovah’s service\Nis a protection for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But more is required to protect our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s vital for all of us to “keep awake”
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,—to be watchful of things
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.15,0:03:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that could pose a danger to us spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What are some of these dangers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.32,0:04:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus mentioned things\Nlike “overeating and heavy drinking
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and anxieties of life.”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.93,0:04:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are some ways\Nthat these things could cause our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.76,0:04:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to “become weighed down”?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let’s talk\Nabout one common cause for anxiety
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,—social isolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt we have never felt as isolated
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.11,0:04:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,as we have during this pandemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.75,0:04:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,True, it has been necessary\Nto isolate ourselves physically
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to prevent the spread of COVID-19.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But if we’re not careful,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.82,0:04:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,we could start\Nto isolate ourselves in other ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe at times, we feel Zoom fatigue,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.97,0:04:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and we even want\Nto isolate ourselves virtually.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s the danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Proverbs 18:1 says:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.41,0:04:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,“Whoever isolates himself
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.21,0:04:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,“pursues his own selfish desires;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,he rejects all practical wisdom.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes effort to reach out\Nto our brothers by telephone,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,by videoconference,\Nor even with an email or text message,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but so often the encouragement\Nthat we receive from doing so
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,makes the effort so worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Often, we receive back\Nmore than what we may have given.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as Jesus said at Acts 20:35:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.95,0:05:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,“There is more happiness in giving
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,than there is in receiving.”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,An article on jw.org entitled
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.39,0:05:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,“How to Deal With Isolation”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.92,0:05:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,made an interesting point\Nunder the heading
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,“Cultivate friendships”:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.66,0:05:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,“Friendships benefit\Nyour mental and emotional health
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.33,0:05:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,“and are even more important\Nwhen face-to-face connections are difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,“If you are confined at home,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.94,0:06:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,“you may be able to use videoconferencing
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,“or voice calls\Nto maintain existing friendships
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.38,0:06:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and build new ones.”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We need our brothers and sisters,\Nand they need us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.59,0:06:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To have a friend, we must be a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.69,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So be a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you reach out to someone this week?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps you can think of a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,whom you haven’t been able\Nto talk with for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The joy of speaking with your friend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,will no doubt calm\Nsome of the anxieties in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We can’t wait to get back\Nto our Kingdom Halls, Assembly Halls,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,to have our large regional conventions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.39,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,special conventions,\Nand even international conventions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.89,0:06:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, we are grateful\Nthat we have other means
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to enjoy these programs, such as Zoom,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,JW Stream and, in some cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.30,0:07:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,TV and radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, most congregations\Nare using Zoom for their meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.31,0:07:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn’t it encouraging\Nto see our brothers’ and sisters’ faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.05,0:07:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate\Nbeing able to see them comment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and see them singing from the heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This also helps us\Nto fight feelings of isolation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.02,0:07:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply turning your camera on and smiling,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,even a simple wave,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,can be such an encouragement to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.03,0:07:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can make it our goal to connect early
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and stay longer after the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We can enjoy visiting\Nwith the friends in breakout rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.65,0:07:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Brothers and sisters,\Nthese are some practical ways
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,that we can fight back\Nagainst feelings of isolation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and the anxiety that isolation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,can create in our hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:08:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Another danger\Nthat Jesus mentioned was heavy drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, there’s nothing wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,with drinking alcohol in moderation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Scriptures describe wine\Nas a gift from God,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,designed to make the “heart rejoice.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.31,0:08:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But some caution is needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:22.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember, Jesus specifically cautioned
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that our hearts\Ncould become “weighed down
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.56,0:08:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,with . . . heavy drinking.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Secular reports indicate that many people
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.76,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,have increased their alcohol consumption\Nduring the pandemic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.03,0:08:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The article “Alcohol Consumption\N—How Can You Stay in Control?”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,on jw.org states:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,“Some people drink more alcohol
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.78,0:08:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,“when they feel stressed,\Nlonely, or simply bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,“Are you drinking more than you used to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.65,0:08:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,“If so, how can you make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,“that your drinking does not get out of hand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.06,0:09:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,or lead to alcohol dependence?”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if a person does not get drunk,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,immoderate drinking\Ncan pose spiritual dangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Isaiah 5:11 says:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,“Woe to those who get up early\Nin the morning to drink alcohol,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.28,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,“who linger late into the evening darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.68,0:09:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,until wine inflames them!”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why these woes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.78,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Note the spiritual consequences\Nin the second half of verse 12:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,“They do not consider\Nthe activity of Jehovah,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and they do not see the work of his hands.”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.93,0:09:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Immoderate drinking\Ncan weigh our hearts down
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.50,0:09:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and cause us to neglect spiritual things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.77,0:09:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It can cause us\Nto slow down in the race for life
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,or even to stop running altogether.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder Jesus specifically mentioned it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.95,0:10:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,when discussing the need\Nto keep awake spiritually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not review that article on jw.org,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.26,0:10:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,which features five tips
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to help us keep alcohol in its proper place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What is another potential danger\Nto our spiritual alertness?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Misuse of social media.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.71,0:10:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There’s been a lot of concern\Nfrom governmental and medical authorities
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,about the effect that social media
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is having on people’s\Nmental and emotional health.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Even more important\Nare the spiritual concerns:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.45,0:10:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,the content, the people,\Nand the amount of time involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.96,0:10:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be addictive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.43,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Brothers and sisters,\Nif you decide to allow your family
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to use social media, please be alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure you have good association
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:11:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,with those who promote good spiritual habits,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.24,0:11:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,whether on screen or off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.31,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The whiteboard animation\N{\i1}{\fs18}{\fnSerif}Be Social-Network Smart
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,provides some good reminders
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.19,0:11:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,on how to be balanced yet cautious\Nwhen using social media.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.96,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What’s the final challenge\Nwe want to consider?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tests of neutrality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With so many different\Nchallenging situations in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and even the threat of war in some countries,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,we need to be sure\Nthat we are not allowing our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,to take sides on these issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How sad it has been\Nto see simple public health measures
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,like wearing masks, handwashing,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,physical distancing, and vaccinations
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,become controversial, even political!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of our brothers and sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,have been influenced by the political views
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.76,0:11:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of those in their community.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.33,0:11:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Some have turned to the Internet
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and have been deeply influenced
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.10,0:12:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,by official-appearing websites
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,filled with highly political propaganda.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.81,0:12:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Brothers and sisters, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.21,0:12:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because something appears
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.55,0:12:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,on an official-looking web page\Non the Internet
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,does not make it true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.75,0:12:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We must guard\Nagainst “the spirit of the world”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and remain neutral.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.86,0:12:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How appropriate are Jesus’ words:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,“Pay attention to yourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.23,0:12:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,that your hearts\Nnever become weighed down.”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.27,0:12:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s keep focused on God’s Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.57,0:12:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,as the only solution\Nto this world’s problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What has helped\Nsome families to keep awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Let’s see as we watch the following video.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.39,0:12:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,During the pandemic,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.66,0:12:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it was definitely difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep a good routine
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was very easy to form bad habits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.83,0:13:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,During isolation,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent more time in front of the computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and it disturbed my sleep pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to make an adjustment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.41,0:13:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,(because with bad habits, you know,\Nthey’re easy to form and hard to break),
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.41,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so I did a little bit\Nof replacement therapy (I call it),
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,where you switch from mindless TV watching
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.08,0:13:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,to something\Nthat’s a little bit more profitable,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,which is our own TV station,\NJW Broadcasting®.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As I spent a lot of time watching television,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a lot of negative information\Nabout vaccination.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt pressure from the media,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I decided\Nnot to get vaccinated for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We often asked Jehovah for guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.64,0:13:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The Governing Body updates were timely
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.24,0:13:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and helped us to make the right decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When the pandemic first started,\NI had a lot of free time on my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:14:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was just on social media all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.56,0:14:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or on technology all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Family worship was an excellent opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,for us to be able to talk about social media\N—to really get Jehovah’s thinking on it—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.43,0:14:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and how we can balance it\Nwhile not eliminating it completely,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so that we controlled it\Nand it didn’t control us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.47,0:14:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a slow process,\Nbut eventually I deleted my social media
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.44,0:14:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and began setting time limits for other apps
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.91,0:14:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,that would take a lot of my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.45,0:14:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Our family decided\Nto spend more time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We played music and danced together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We played board games\Nand went for walks together in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.19,0:14:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That helped us\Nto reduce the time we used for social media.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided to keep my schedule busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.57,0:14:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,so I started a few new hobbies,\Nlike knitting and gardening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.94,0:14:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw a lot of benefit in staying close\Nto the congregation through Zoom,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:14:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,even though Zoom is not easy for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:14:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to spend time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.95,0:15:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,with people who were going\Nthrough the same thing as I was,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,was really beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We could all talk\Nabout what we were dealing with
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.79,0:15:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and encourage each other as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We arranged\Nonline Bible-based games through Zoom{\i1}{\fs18}{\fnSerif}.{\r} 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it nice to use Zoom\Nto connect with the congregation
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,for events that were planned\Nby those in our hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of them were interviews
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,with those who have been\Nin our hall for a long time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.74,0:15:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,so it was nice to hear those experiences
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and be able to draw closer to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.61,0:15:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,During the pandemic,\NI would reach out to others
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.81,0:15:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,—either a phone call\Nor a little card or a text message
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,or just dropping something off\Nat someone’s door—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.72,0:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and it helped me to feel closer\Nto my brothers and sisters too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Governing Body updates\Nwere an absolute lifeline.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They were something that really helped us\Nto focus all of our activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,As parents, they helped us\Nto have clear direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.83,0:15:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so we felt like we were guided\Nthrough the whole pandemic
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.74,0:15:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and encouraged at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:16:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I also have been able to see Jehovah\Nanswer my personal prayers even more so
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.28,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and see just how he\Nis holding all of us up
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,during this difficult time,\Nbecause I don’t think any of us
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,could get through this pandemic without him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We are proud of these families\Nfor keeping awake to spiritual dangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.09,0:16:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you notice\Nhow they counteracted social isolation?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.23,0:16:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They have reached out to others regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,They use videoconferencing
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,to stay close\Nto their congregations and dear friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.31,0:16:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you notice how they addressed\Ntheir use of social media?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They talked about it as a family
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.55,0:16:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and decided either to reduce the time spent
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,or eliminate it completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.22,0:16:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They have also increased\Nthe time they spend together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,including enjoyable outdoor activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.36,0:16:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And how did they handle tests of neutrality?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They prayed to Jehovah\Nand trusted the information
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.67,0:17:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,provided by “the faithful and discreet slave”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,in making their own personal decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Very soon, Jehovah’s day\Nwill come upon all the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.85,0:17:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It’s vital that we keep awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.15,0:17:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time\Nto become spiritually drowsy or distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember Jesus’ words at Luke 21:36:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,“Keep awake, then,\Nall the time making supplication
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.90,0:17:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,“that you may succeed\Nin escaping all these things
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.44,0:17:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that must occur and in standing\Nbefore the Son of man.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,By earnestly supplicating Jehovah
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and applying the fine direction\Nwe are receiving,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,we will be successful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.55,0:17:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,From the World Headquarters\Nof Jehovah’s Witnesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.12,0:17:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,this is JW Broadcasting.
